{"tid":581680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發現連登仔都係精神勝利者","createTime":"2018-03-05T14:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T00:19:23.000Z","uid":16951,"like":38,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"194cc80cd9d3a46b433ae8fe481c20c486c2bcd6","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"大部份講到習近平想復辟唔關自己事咁<br />\n實則維尼每捉一步棋 對香港隨時有影響<br />\n你思想上認為香港獨立 但事實仲行緊虛有其名嘅一國兩制<br />\n咁快已經好似阿Q咁撚樣 香港死硬啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一條友做唔到啲乜 多幾十萬個連登仔實事實幹或者香港就有救喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cf21117b4bdff49fcfe3a1eb2f9c730018da2b0","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"感覺就好似上緊毒果facrbook page<br />\n個個置身事外 明明同自己嘅生活有關係 都係好似none of my business <br />\n將來天琦 陳浩天或者唔知邊個真係要搞一場革命 我都幾肯定呢道又會有班人係咁屌人政棍 之後又要返工不了<br />\n我知又會有人笑柒我做到啲乜 呢點又係連登仔好on9嘅位 一比人篤中就搵野屌返人轉頭<br />\n但至少我做返我會去做嘅先 未來喺我地手呀連登仔"},{"pid":"4258e9fed34b49d874bb2e256d3873b1fc45cc11","tid":581680,"uid":51129,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"唔好講咁多喇，撐下獨立post先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日都唔對全世界宣布香港獨立 仲等幾時<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/366243/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/366243/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"c6f97009e62f366f53ca1058e8262b2970ea2f05","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4258e9fed34b49d874bb2e256d3873b1fc45cc11","tid":581680,"uid":51129,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"唔好講咁多喇，撐下獨立post先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日都唔對全世界宣布香港獨立 仲等幾時<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/366243/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/366243/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:28:21.000Z","msg":"入面有啲連登仔都好有心 諗得好詳細<br />\n但係 精神長存 主權盪然無存"},{"pid":"05ab39838435a28e283b59214b8c9ab32edbc380","tid":581680,"uid":15984,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"陳浩天既武裝起義宣言<br />\n獲連登仔破紀錄讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52996b7511e3b46fabdce622666d9a1065ac258b","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05ab39838435a28e283b59214b8c9ab32edbc380","tid":581680,"uid":15984,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"陳浩天既武裝起義宣言<br />\n獲連登仔破紀錄讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"每個人都好想變 但無奈成個香港都充斥住阿Q精神 我唔係想怪連登仔 只係希望大家認清事實"},{"pid":"5b382f832b14a90e998407f6792c133870aa7397","tid":581680,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"35a2c87a2098946ea5a59edde35318a32da9e9c1","tid":581680,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:33:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e9b2d9be0e067e68556f30f30de7a0c9c97f5bb","tid":581680,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔好再遲啲先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0826ba76c341359d521456830c69b8b8ca4a3203","tid":581680,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"一講，就話阿邊個邊個要打官司同坐監<br />\n好似當年希特拉同孫中山未坐過咁，淆底就縮入房啦"},{"pid":"99c68feec8c434c88064c7b7538a9fca3754830f","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3e9b2d9be0e067e68556f30f30de7a0c9c97f5bb","tid":581680,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:36:07.000Z","msg":"樓豬唔好再遲啲先發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:43:34.000Z","msg":"其實發現咗好耐 係維尼單野個個置身事外咁款我先開post想大家清醒下<br />\n老實講喺呢家呢個環境下 我都好無力 無論係未來要結婚生仔定推動香港民主化，獨立云云<br />\n但我永遠都覺得 有能力就行多一步 或者呢一步會成為好多事嘅里程碑"},{"pid":"11bfed6b5667ed41b7e9573bb1ead013ae4e75af","tid":581680,"uid":15984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"52996b7511e3b46fabdce622666d9a1065ac258b","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05ab39838435a28e283b59214b8c9ab32edbc380","tid":581680,"uid":15984,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"陳浩天既武裝起義宣言<br />\n獲連登仔破紀錄讚好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"每個人都好想變 但無奈成個香港都充斥住阿Q精神 我唔係想怪連登仔 只係希望大家認清事實"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:45:51.000Z","msg":"讚好 = 做左"},{"pid":"aa59418ba821e61c32481f6090d7b15572e1776b","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b382f832b14a90e998407f6792c133870aa7397","tid":581680,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:32:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"我答唔到你 或者咁講<br />\n我有位去左北京拍電影嘅朋友話國內人覺得維尼係想做第二個毛賊 毛賊擔正嘅時期全國有幾多天災人禍你睇返歷史都知 咁如果維尼的確企圖成為再世毛澤東 我地有咩後果其實唔多唔少都預計到"},{"pid":"0cbca11c42ca8b197a506d4de517900536b98876","tid":581680,"uid":106375,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:48:21.000Z","msg":"無論係普通市民定連登仔都好<br />\n未真正燒埋黎都唔會理"},{"pid":"8266a014333f68b7ae9be12f9d557020a41e8e60","tid":581680,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:53:18.000Z","msg":"連登仔網上鳩吹就叻，放返底個鍵盤就只係一個失敗小毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8291bd69e789547f63d92e1cc9712a5781226dfd","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0826ba76c341359d521456830c69b8b8ca4a3203","tid":581680,"uid":49392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:38:24.000Z","msg":"一講，就話阿邊個邊個要打官司同坐監<br />\n好似當年希特拉同孫中山未坐過咁，淆底就縮入房啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:56:09.000Z","msg":"呢樣係值得討論<br />\n法治成為規範 一來係教育上嘅灌輸 二來就係前途<br />\n孫中山 孟德拉坐完監依然有support 依家？你坐個監出到嚟都唔知仲有無人記得你 無咗號召力 又要留住個案底 其實無得怪責<br />\n所以我好佩服g峰嗰堆人 係人都話呢班口講民主 自決 獨立嘅人呃飯食 我心諗入撚左去踎監喇屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47c1854cb47cecf4d56cdd8d92eaaa3200aa6af","tid":581680,"uid":51129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4258e9fed34b49d874bb2e256d3873b1fc45cc11","tid":581680,"uid":51129,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:24:40.000Z","msg":"唔好講咁多喇，撐下獨立post先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日都唔對全世界宣布香港獨立 仲等幾時<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/366243/1?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/366243/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T14:57:44.000Z","msg":"邊個負皮我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n獨立post都負皮咁係咩意思先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8f2314d26befa0ce58b2d55697fe01d3288b8e","tid":581680,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T15:25:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"74cb2dcf925ee0fc1606bfa9a10e012d941f447a","tid":581680,"uid":16951,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8b8f2314d26befa0ce58b2d55697fe01d3288b8e","tid":581680,"uid":103127,"like